<section class="programming" id="investment">
  <div class="container container-narrow">
    <h2 class="section-title text-center">Year-Round Programming</h2>
    <p class="lead text-center text-muted">
      When the village season ends, the property keeps working.
    </p>

    <div class="programming-content">
      <div class="programming-block">
        <h3>Hospitality Stays</h3>
        <p>
          Outside the village season and the investor priority window, the property
          is available for bookings. Guests experience the jungle, the surf, and the
          community culture in a boutique setting. The thirteen structures allow for
          a range of group sizes and stay configurations.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="programming-block">
        <h3>Curated Retreats</h3>
        <p>
          Throughout the year, the property hosts focused retreats in wellness,
          leadership, creativity, professional development, and more. Retreats are
          curated for quality and cultural fit. This is not a generic venue-for-hire
          model. Every retreat group is selected for alignment with the property's
          mission and community culture.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="programming-block">
        <h3>Impact Residencies</h3>
        <p>
          The property hosts residencies focused on human and environmental flourishing.
          Researchers, artists, educators, and practitioners are welcomed for extended
          stays. Residencies deepen the property's mission, generate meaningful output,
          and build the community of people connected to Rosemary Dream over time.
          Applications for the impact residency program open seasonally.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="programming-block">
        <h3>Real Assets in an Uncertain Market</h3>
        <p>
          Land does not disappear. Buildings hold value through cycles. Florianópolis
          has seen growing international interest as a digital nomad community and
          tourism destination in Brazil. The property's multiple structures create
          flexibility that a single building cannot match. Demand trends have been
          positive, though past conditions are not a guarantee of future results.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="investment-disclaimer">
      <p>
        <strong>Important:</strong> This is not investment advice. Real estate involves
        risk. Values can decrease. Regulatory environments change. Conduct your own
        due diligence with qualified professionals before making any investment decision.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
